# Knol — Docker build context exclusions
.git/
.github/
**/.git/
**/target/
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/out/
**/.turbo/
**/dist/
**/coverage/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo

# Local env/secrets (allow examples)
.env*
!.env.example
**/.env*
!**/.env.example

# Local docs/assets that are not required for runtime images
brand/
*.md
LICENSE*
